	getaddrinfo() manpage says it's reentrant, but it definitely crashes
	with two threads in the function at the same time.  it's possible
	i'm doing something evil, but i don't think so, and this will ensure
	only one thread is calling getaddrinfo() at a time.  well, unless
	another panel plugin calls it... *sigh*

