2005-04-16  Brian Tarricone <bjt23@cornell.edu>

	* this code totally doesn't do anything yet.  it probably doesn't even
	compile.  but it's a start, and putting it up in svn means i have to
	follow through with it.  the architecture isn't completely fleshed
	out; i'm prototyping as i go along.  comments welcome.

